    "2. Constructed a custom Hybrid SAM-U-Net architecture.\n",
    "3. Computed class weights from the training dataset.\n",
    "4. Trained the model using weighted BCE-Dice loss.\n",
    "5. Evaluated performance using Dice Score and IoU.\n",
